---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="about - octanebula.dev">
  <article class="md">
    <div class="filebar">
      <span class="path">~ / about.md</span>
      <span class="mode">read-only</span>
    </div>

    <h1>octavian</h1>
    <p class="tagline">aka @octanebula. CS student. Roblox dev. Occasional software freak.</p>

    <h2>about</h2>
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Karlo. 19, born and currently slowly being crushed alive by my Computer
      Science degree at the University of Zagreb. Online I go by Octavian and
      use the @octanebula tag basically everywhere.
    </p>
    <p>
      I've been doing UI/UX design for Roblox games for the past four years.
      Started by grinding HiddenDevs commissions. Eventually got tired of being
      underpaid and pivoted to working with people I actually like. That ended
      up being a much better idea.
    </p>

    <h2>currently</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>co-owner of <a href="https://www.roblox.com/communities/5670504/TOPLINE-STUDIOS-INC"><strong>Topline Studios</strong></a>, where I lead game and UI design on our game <em>Mafia</em></li>
      <li>UI designer at <a href="https://www.roblox.com/communities/33895110/Marmots-Oven"><strong>Marmot's Oven</strong></a>, working on <em>Steel Crossfire</em></li>
      <li>studying my CS undergrad and pretending I'll be productive over winter break</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>stack</h2>
    <pre><code>languages   python, c, java (thanks, FER)
design      photoshop, not figma, after effects (badly)
engines     roblox studio
os          arch + hyprland, because i hate myself in a fun way
editor      vscode. yes, i know. this will anger purists.
            vim and emacs got pacman -Rns'd off my system and i sleep great.</code></pre>

    <h2>hobbies</h2>
    <details class="hobbies">
      <summary>uh oh here it comes</summary>
      <ul>
        <li>programming</li>
        <li>playing game dev tycoon irl</li>
        <li>messing with linux</li>
        <li>gaming</li>
        <li>hating on Rust <span class="aside">(just admit you suck at using malloc lmfao)</span></li>
        <li>ui design</li>
        <li>running random models found on huggingface</li>
        <li>sci-fi</li>
        <li>working on random projects</li>
        <li>exploring niche media</li>
        <li>watching anime when i run out of ideas</li>
        <li>doomscrolling during critical lectures</li>
        <li>pondering philosophy while showering</li>
        <li>listening to indie music</li>
        <li>occasionally breaking software</li>
        <li>wasting time on side quests</li>
        <li>touching grass</li>
        <li>probably more stuff i forgot idk</li>
      </ul>
    </details>

    <h2>elsewhere</h2>
    <ul class="links">
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/octanebula">xitter</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/octanebula">github</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.roblox.com/users/162871269/profile">roblox</a></li>
      <li><span class="wip-email">hi@octanebula.dev<span class="wip-bubble">wip!</span></span></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>why this page exists</h2>
    <blockquote>
      I kept procrastinating on rebuilding my site. Then I got verified, then
      I paid for Claude Max, and the guilt finally outweighed the laziness.
    </blockquote>

    <p class="signoff">— end of file —</p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .md {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--fg);
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .filebar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(16, 20, 42, 0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .filebar .path::before { content: '📄  '; }
  .filebar .mode {
    color: var(--tag-shipped);
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding: 0.05rem 0.45rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  .md > h1,
  .md > h2,
  .md > h3,
  .md > p,
  .md > ul,
  .md > pre,
  .md > blockquote,
  .md > details {
    background: rgba(16, 20, 42, 0.55);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.35rem 1.1rem;
  }
  .md > h1 + p { padding-top: 0; }
  .md > p + p { padding-top: 0; }

  .md > :last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* obsidian-style read mode: hash markers reveal on hover */
  .md h1,
  .md h2,
  .md h3 {
    position: relative;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .md h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; padding-top: 1.1rem; padding-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .md h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .md h3 { font-size: 1rem;    padding-top: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 0.3rem; }

  .md h1, .md h2, .md h3 { transition: padding-left 140ms ease; }
  .md h1:hover { padding-left: 2.5rem; }
  .md h2:hover { padding-left: 2.8rem; }
  .md h3:hover { padding-left: 4.2rem; }

  .md h1::before,
  .md h2::before,
  .md h3::before {
    position: absolute;
    left: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 140ms ease;
    font-weight: 400;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .md h1::before { content: '#\00a0'; }
  .md h2::before { content: '##\00a0'; }
  .md h3::before { content: '###\00a0'; }
  .md h1:hover::before,
  .md h2:hover::before,
  .md h3:hover::before { opacity: 0.55; }
  .md h1:hover::before,
  .md h2:hover::before,
  .md h3:hover::before { opacity: 0.55; }

  .md p { color: var(--fg); }
  .md .tagline { color: var(--fg-dim); font-style: italic; padding-top: 0; }

  .md ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
  }
  .md ul li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
  }
  .md ul li::before {
    content: '-';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .md ul li:hover::before { color: var(--accent); }

  .md strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .md em { color: var(--fg); font-style: italic; }
  .md a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }

  /* obsidian-style: inline marks reveal on hover */
  .md p strong::before, .md p strong::after,
  .md p em::before, .md p em::after,
  .md p code::before, .md p code::after,
  .md li strong::before, .md li strong::after,
  .md li em::before, .md li em::after,
  .md li code::before, .md li code::after {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    opacity: 0;
    font-size: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: normal;
    transition: opacity 140ms ease, font-size 140ms ease;
  }
  .md p strong::before, .md p strong::after,
  .md li strong::before, .md li strong::after { content: '**'; }
  .md p em::before, .md p em::after,
  .md li em::before, .md li em::after { content: '*'; }
  .md p code::before, .md p code::after,
  .md li code::before, .md li code::after { content: '`'; }

  .md p strong:hover::before, .md p strong:hover::after,
  .md p em:hover::before, .md p em:hover::after,
  .md p code:hover::before, .md p code:hover::after,
  .md li strong:hover::before, .md li strong:hover::after,
  .md li em:hover::before, .md li em:hover::after,
  .md li code:hover::before, .md li code:hover::after {
    opacity: 0.55;
    font-size: inherit;
  }

  .md code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    background: rgba(7, 9, 26, 0.6);
    padding: 0.05rem 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.86em;
  }

  .md pre {
    overflow-x: auto;
    background: rgba(7, 9, 26, 0.7);
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  .md pre code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    white-space: pre;
    display: block;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .md pre code { font-size: 0.74rem; }
  }

  .md blockquote {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    position: relative;
  }
  .md blockquote::before {
    content: '>';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.3rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 140ms ease;
  }
  .md blockquote:hover::before { opacity: 0.55; }
  .md blockquote:hover { padding-left: 1.6rem; }
  .md blockquote { transition: padding-left 140ms ease; }

  .md details.hobbies { padding-top: 0.6rem; padding-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .md details.hobbies summary {
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    text-decoration: underline dotted;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .md details.hobbies summary:hover { color: var(--fg); }
  .md details.hobbies summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .md details.hobbies summary::before {
    content: '▸ ';
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    transition: transform 140ms ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .md details.hobbies[open] summary::before {
    content: '▾ ';
  }
  .md details.hobbies summary:hover { filter: brightness(1.15); }
  .md details.hobbies ul { padding-left: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .md details.hobbies ul li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0.25rem 0;
  }
  .md details.hobbies ul li::before {
    content: '-';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .md .aside {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* extend inline mark hover behavior into details */
  .md details li strong::before, .md details li strong::after,
  .md details li em::before, .md details li em::after,
  .md details li code::before, .md details li code::after {
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    opacity: 0;
    font-size: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: normal;
    transition: opacity 140ms ease, font-size 140ms ease;
  }
  .md details li strong::before, .md details li strong::after { content: '**'; }
  .md details li em::before, .md details li em::after { content: '*'; }
  .md details li code::before, .md details li code::after { content: '`'; }
  .md details li strong:hover::before, .md details li strong:hover::after,
  .md details li em:hover::before, .md details li em:hover::after,
  .md details li code:hover::before, .md details li code:hover::after {
    opacity: 0.55;
    font-size: inherit;
  }

  .md .signoff {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    padding-top: 1.4rem;
  }
  .md .links {
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
</style>
